lead_paragraph: Tori Jankoska scored 22 points, including four free throws in the final 10 seconds, to lift No. 24 Michigan State past Cal State Northridge for a 63-59 win.

headline.print_headline: Jankoska Lifts No. 24 Michigan St. Women Past CS Northridge
